            <abstract>
                <p>
                    <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
                     and
                    <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
                     are assured that their petition has been received and their complaints about
                    local officials will be dealt with; they are urged to maintain peace and
                    productivity in their areas.</p>
