    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1655_brd_ac_r.jpg"/>

            <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
                <p>الله اکبر</p>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
                <p>God is great</p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
                <p><lb/> زبده الاقران
                    <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتمداس</persName>
                     چودهری و
                    <persName ref="#parasRam">پرسرام</persName>
                     قانونگوی پرگنه
                    <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
                     را انها آنکه
                    <lb/>عرضداشتی که فرستاده بودنند رسید مضمون معلوم شد و در باب اجاره داران و
                    <lb/>متصدیان پرگنه مذکور مرقوم بود چه آنها اینطور خیالهای عبث عبث می کنند الحال
                    <lb/>می باید که برسیدن نوشته دلاسای و تسلی
                     آنها نمایند که آینده خاطر خودها جمع نموده سازند بجای خودها
                    <lb/>آباد باشد و در آنچه رضامندی بهبودی آنها است پرداخته خواهد شد و نیز در
                    ینولا
                    <lb/>نوشته ها از حضور پرنور
                    <space/>
                     آمده اند انشاالله وقتی ما در آنجا خواهم رسید حقایق نوشته های
                    <lb/>اظهار نموده خواهد شد عرض که
                    <unclear>بهمدردی</unclear>
                     خاطر رعایا جمع نمایند که هیچ وجه دغدغه و ملاحظه
                    <lb/>بخاطر
                    <unclear>برده</unclear>
                     ندهند. درین باب تاکید دانند تحریر فی التاریخ
                    <date calendar="#julus">
                        <num>۱۰</num>
                     شهر ربیع الثانی سنه
                    <num>۲۸</num>
                    </date>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
                <p><lb/>Eminent among Contemporaries
                    <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
                    <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> and
                    <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
                    <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungo</ref> of <ref type="glossary"
                        target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
                    <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>
                     are informed that
                    <lb/>the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_arzdasht">ʿarzdasht</ref> that they
                    had sent has arrived and the contents have been noted. Regarding the <ref
                        type="glossary" target="#gl_ijaradar">ijaradars</ref> and
                    <lb/>officials of the said <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana"
                        >pargana</ref>, it was written that they have the most absurd ideas. Now
                    <lb/>it is necessary that on the receipt of this exalted note, they should be
                    consoled and soothed, so that in future their minds are content and well-settled in their place.
                    <lb/>And all that causes their satisfaction and well-being will be done. Also,
                    at this time,
                    <lb/>the notes from the radiant Lord have arrived [so], God willing, when we
                    reach there, the rights of all that is
                    <lb/>written of will be declared. You are requested to settle the minds of the
                    peasants so that there shall be no cause for their having thoughts of disturbance or quarrel.
                    <lb/>Know this as settled. Written on the
                    <date calendar="#julus">10th of the month of Rabiʿ al-sani in the 28th regnal
                        year</date>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="endorsements" rend="right margin">
                <p><lb/>زبده الاقرانانا
                    <lb/>این شکایت عبث عبث خودها را در وسواس انداخته اند
                    <lb/>شما دلآسای ان غریبان بسیار بسیار بکنید هر چه
                    <unclear>آنها</unclear>
                    <lb/>خود رضامند باشند چنان خواهم کرد چون
                    <lb/>مشقت آنها را ضایع بخواهم کرد آنها
                    <lb/>را رضامند و
                    <app><rdg cert="medium">شاکر</rdg>
                        <rdg cert="low">ساکن</rdg></app>
                    نگاه
                    <gap/>
                     داشت
                    <lb/>آنها را خود
                    <gap/>
                     هار فرستاد اند
                    <lb/>و بجا و مقام خود
                     آورده
                     <gap></gap>
                    <lb/>بسیار بسیار بسیار بکنید
                    <gap/><note>The text continues onto the top margin.</note>
                    <lb/>در باب آمدن
                    کسی آنها
                    <gap/>
                     بخدمت
                    <lb/>وزارت پناه معلوم نموده از پروانه ان
                    <lb/>که سیادت پناه می رسیده معلوم خواهد شد
                    <lb/>مطابق ان بعمل آورند و
                    <gap/>
                    <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
                <p><lb/>Eminent among Contemporaries,
                    <lb/>these very absurd complaints have thrown you into doubt.
                    <lb/>You should console these poor people very, very much. Whatever
                    <lb/>would satisfy [them] I will do. When
                    <lb/>I shall destroy their difficulties, it should keep them
                    <lb/>satisfied and <app><rdg cert="medium">thankul
                     </rdg><rdg cert="low">resident</rdg></app>
                    <gap/>.
                    <lb/>They
                    <gap/>
                     have been sent.
                    <lb/>And accomplishing and settling [it] yourself, 
                    <lb/>make <gap/> very, very, very much.
                    <gap/>
                    <lb/>In the matter of the coming of some person of them
                    <gap/>
                     to serve
                    <lb/>the Refuge of Ministry becoming known, from each <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">parvana</ref>
                    <lb/>that reaches the Refuge of Sublimity, it will be known.
                    <lb/>Do as ordered in this [order] and
                    <gap/>. <g ref="#faqt">Nothing further</g>. </p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="top left">
                <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                            <persName ref="#abdusSalam">عبد السلام</persName>
                             بن محمد
                            <gap/>
                             خان غلام سلطان
                            <persName ref="#muradBakhsh">مراد بخش</persName>
                            <unclear>
                                <persName ref="#shahJahan">شاه جهان</persName>
                            </unclear>
                            <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">۱۰۵۴</date>
                        </mentioned></stamp></p>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
                <p><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned>
                            <persName ref="#abdusSalam">Abdussalam</persName>, son of Muhammad
                            <gap/>
                             Khan, slave of Sultan
                            <persName ref="#muradBakhsh">Murad Bakhsh</persName>, [son of]
                            <unclear>
                                <persName ref="#shahJahan">Shah Jahan</persName>
                            </unclear>
                            <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1054</date>
                        </mentioned></stamp>
                    <note>For a variation of this seal, see "Order of an official of Prince Murad
                        Bakhsh to Purshottam Das."</note>
                </p>
            </div>
            <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1655_brd_ac_v.jpg"/>
            <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes">
                <p> پروانه بندگان رفعت و ایالت دستگاه
                    <unclear>احور</unclear>
                    صاحب جیو
                    <unclear>آمار</unclear>
                    دلاسای رعایا پرگنه بجانب
                    <persName ref="#gujaratRai">گجرات رای</persName>
                    شده نمود بتاریخ
                    <date calendar="#julus">
                        <num>۱۳</num>
                         شهر ربیع الثانی سنه
                        <num>۲۸</num>
                    </date>
                    <gap/>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5">
                <p><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref> of the servants of the exalted and fortunate government of <unclear>Ahwar</unclear><note>This is presumably part of a name or title.</note> Sahib <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref>, 
                    <unclear>the investigation of</unclear> the consolation of the subjects of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana"
                    >pargana</ref> was done on behalf of <persName ref="#gujaratRai">Gujarat Rai</persName>. On the date of <date calendar="#julus">13 [of the] month of Rabiʿ al-sani in the 28th year</date> <gap></gap></p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
